name: INFINITE CHAOS | ISSUE 2/4
description:
a never ending torrent of random glyphs constrained to a single hue, representing a moment from the life of those who share an interest in the the special skills you prefer to spend your time on

do you see how each has its own blind spots scattered amongst its own sea of illumination? what are your personal blind spots at this point in time and space, and what are you doing to light them up?

this is an open edition to celebrate 5k followers. remaining copies will be burnt in 36 hours, and the number of remaining editions will be used as an input variable in a future nft
